{"tid":1633044,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"石硤尾呢間垃圾茶記唔好去~","createTime":"2019-10-07T02:04:16.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-08T12:44:40.000Z","uid":299355,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"1a73d3f2cb70507076a508c81275a315a363026b","tid":1633044,"uid":299355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:04:16.000Z","msg":"石硤尾呢間垃圾茶記唔好去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkon9agroup/permalink/3184873894886986/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgroups%2Fhkon9agroup%2Fpermalink%2F3184873894886986%2F&d=GDC1bQ0cPxo7GxZf5EwJ4gKWJX65Gw4YGtkQ1cmlXhw%3D&h=757d5a98\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/groups/hkon9agroup/permalink/3184873894886986/</a>"},{"pid":"24b0f2a75de4568e5166d2923db4232b748e0d7c","tid":1633044,"uid":207553,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:04:36.000Z","msg":"既然連仔唔整英文台,我地就自制英文台<br />\n<a href=\"http://lih.kg/ejrhgT\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://lih.kg/ejrhgT</a><br />\n#1 回覆 - 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"674af7ad7372fc57feff9fb55f3c69fac30838ae","tid":1633044,"uid":287461,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:05:07.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://lihkg.com/thread/1633005/page/1\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lihkg.com/thread/1633005/page/1</a><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">和理非戰場－面具人鏈</span></span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: small;\">外國嘅人好幸福，一出世就生活係民主國家，有部分人根本唔會明點解我地爭取民主要用裝修、神獸（唔好高估外國人嘅智力，佢地睇野好表面）。</span><br />\n<br />\n有位巴講得好啱，我地<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">之所以漸漸少咗國際支持，係因為和理非戰場越來越細</span></span>。冇和理非嘅活動吸引佢地嘅眼球，餘下嘅只有神獸同裝修。<br />\n<br />\n咁所以，我地可以搞返個<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">面具人鏈</span></span>，表達我地不畏反蒙面法，不畏極權嘅精神。<br />\n人鏈活動一直都比較少人被人拉，比起遊行更適合一家大細出席<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n而且我地日日遊行，係外國人眼中好悶㗎。<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: blue;\">要有多啲gimmick佢地先會重新關注</span></span>。<br />\n時間、地點我唔知應該點定<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，但如果真係搞面具人鏈，我地可以帶上自製嘅四川面譜、facepainting、動物面膜、超人、Mario、多啦A夢、V煞⋯⋯冇嘅話純戴口罩都得，不過口罩上可以畫野。總之約精彩越好玩越好<br />\n我地<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: limegreen;\">依家好需要一個嘉年華式抗爭</span></span>去緩和下大家嘅情緒，同獲得國際認同。好似之前雷射革命咁。<br />\n<br />\n如果各位手足覺得呢個建議ok，就開多另一個po去講時間地點啦。<br />\n（大家都要考慮一個問題就係，面具人鏈會唔會被狗拉，如果會嘅話⋯⋯都係諗諗先。畢竟expect一家大細出席，怕會全家被告）<br />\n<br />\np牌求推"},{"pid":"4015c0a49be869feba3ab3f0a546f11b815fa966","tid":1633044,"uid":288523,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:05:27.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"73f3f63b1fc0b85f3cf66570b09ed4c24981d843","tid":1633044,"uid":284064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:06:40.000Z","msg":"P牌推唔到"},{"pid":"96a9a374f1b9385cc8bc544b5c9e4b27e78c5678","tid":1633044,"uid":284064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:10:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"51ce714f825ae23eecb7f21bf8565f795bdb92cd","tid":1633044,"uid":299355,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"96a9a374f1b9385cc8bc544b5c9e4b27e78c5678","tid":1633044,"uid":284064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:10:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/shocking.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-07T02:51:05.000Z","msg":"神獸們手腳真係快<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"891c4a084f055096f431b494c52d5bd18f7cf702","tid":1633044,"uid":62891,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:38:16.000Z","msg":"今日間野都冇開<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"068442aae750161011918536686c18979a7b4b86","tid":1633044,"uid":117232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-08T12:44:40.000Z","msg":"呢間野真心好難食 連檸茶都可以沖得難飲<br />\n唔明點解可以生存咁耐"}]}